WEBVTT

00:00:04.699 --> 00:00:09.399
Shah Rukh Khan: Food and happiness 
have an intense relationship …

00:00:09.400 --> 00:00:12.319
not just eating, even cooking
good food can make you happy.

00:00:12.320 --> 00:00:15.199
This is what a world-renowned
Indian chef believes in.

00:00:15.200 --> 00:00:18.199
He has a Michelin-starred
restaurant in New York.

00:00:18.200 --> 00:00:20.759
The Queen of England,
has his cook book.

00:00:20.760 --> 00:00:24.399
His cooking has been praised
by President Obama.

00:00:24.400 --> 00:00:29.199
And it all started in Amritsar,
in his grandmother’s kitchen.

00:00:29.200 --> 00:00:31.105
Today to share his recipe for happiness,